Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:21.72,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,A girl in class 3 died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.75,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Everybody's talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:28.06,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,When she fell down the stairs, her umbrella \Nflew out of her hand and impaled her throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.37,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:33.63,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,It was so horrific that the witnesses were told to never speak of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.10,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Wasn't she a class officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.99,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I heard her mother died in \Nan accident that same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.25,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Do you think it's that curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.60,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,You know of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.44,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It's the school's \Nmost famous secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:50.18,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,The curse of class 3, and the story that started it all 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.31,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.73,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Does that mean it's going \Nto happen again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:58.12,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Who knows. Nothing \Nhappened last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.78,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Once it's started, a person \Ndies every month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:06.25,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Yeah. At least one person connected to the class dies per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.36,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Not just students?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.41,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Families are at risk too, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.19,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Especially parents and siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.25,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.59,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,One of the seniors in my \Nkendo club is in class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.79,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,He told me in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.22,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,He seemed completely \Nskeptical, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.97,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,But someone actually died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.39,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.66,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,It's probably best to \Nstay away from that class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:30.05,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah.
