Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:58.83,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakakibara. \NHow's your lung doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.21,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.22,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,But you witnessed \Nsuch a gruesome event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.96,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,That sort of thing \Ncan affect your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.05,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.80,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,My little brother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:13.97,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,He's in the same class as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.47,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Mizuno Takeru. \NHe plays basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.50,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Are you here for your checkup?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.57,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.31,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Right. Let's talk afterwards, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:31.06,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I should be home by now. My shift ended hours ago, but things keep coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.94,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Something weird is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.24,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,There was also \Nthat other incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:40.12,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,About that girl who \Ndied here in April?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.05,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Try not to stress \Nyourself over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.62,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,If you do have to be \Nhospitalized again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:49.22,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to take \Nextra good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.81,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Great. Thanks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.36,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,All right, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:58.73,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,This is nothing that should \Naffect school attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.91,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,However, no strenuous \Nactivities just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.73,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Let's keep an eye on things \Nfor another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.83,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.45,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.91,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:18.11,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It looks like you won't \Nhave to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.45,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Aw, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:25.04,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,It's a little late, but do you \Nwant to grab lunch somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:34.36,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,So Fujioka Misaki was the cousin of that girl with the eyepatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:42.92,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Anyway, I rarely talk to my little brother, but he did tell me a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:47.29,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,It seems your class has \Nsome special circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.42,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Special circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.88,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:53.41,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,He wouldn't explain \Nanything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.90,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,You know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,About the circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.29,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I know something's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.15,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,but nobody will tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.99,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:09.11,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,My little brother \Nseemed to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:10.76,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Though, that's just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.45,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:16.27,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,He doesn't think that the incident last week was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.93,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Not an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.91,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,And that's why he's scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.35,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.27,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.98,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, have you heard of \Nsomeone named Misaki Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.39,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.91,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Misaki... Mei? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,A girl in class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Has your brother \Never mentioned her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:51.56,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I told you, we don't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:55.66,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Actually, the girl with the \Neyepatch I told you about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.66,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,is named Misaki Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.24,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:03.54,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,So, Sakakibara, \Ndo you like this Mei girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.25,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.98,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's just... something's \Nbeen bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:12.63,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Something about her is different from the rest of the class.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.19,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Isn't that what it \Nmeans to like someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.93,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.74,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.55,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,What's so different \Nabout this Mei girl, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.88,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,She's a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:33.57,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,At first, I thought she was \Nbeing bullied by the other kids,{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:36.15,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,but I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.77,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's more like \Nthey're all scared of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.38,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Scared of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.50,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Well, not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:47.68,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Someone told me not to involve \Nmyself with things that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.24,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Things that don't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.68,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,She claims nobody else \Nin the class can see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.12,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Right after she told me, \Nthat accident happened.{merged}{he says "last week" but I think we've made that point clear enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.27,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,If you think about it logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.43,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,it seems like a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:07.34,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I mean, there's nothing \Nconnecting those two events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.13,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.52,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,There's one more thing \Nthat's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.83,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,They say it happened 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.98,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Have you heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.48,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Not until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.87,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,But I went to South Middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:36.78,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I still don't know what \Nit has to do with all this,{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:39.22,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,but I can't help thinking \Nthere's some connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.95,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.18,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,This whole thing is turning \Ninto quite the horror story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:50.05,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,So, do you want me to \Nask my brother about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.69,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,You're going to school \Ntomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.99,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.70,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,If I hear anything, \NI'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.32,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,When's your next checkup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.06,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,This Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.31,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,June 6th, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.56,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I don't think Damien{ Thorn} \Nis in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:09.05,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.28,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Especially where unusual \Naccidents are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:24.61,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think Damien{ Thorn} \Nis in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.77,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.09,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Oh! Look who I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.72,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Hiya, Kouichi! Skipping school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.74,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No, I just left the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:42.08,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What about you? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.55,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.02,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You're quite the actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.62,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,I hate to say it, but \NI'm happy you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.05,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.91,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Yeah! It means my hard work \Nin the club is paying off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.85,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Which club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.07,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,To be, or not to be:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.19,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,that is the question.{aye(I) there's the point}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.43,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Oh, you're in the theater club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.29,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Yep! With Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.05,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Izumi... Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.92,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Akazawa Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.93,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,She tends to be a bit dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.27,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,It shows in her acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.77,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,But she's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:28.63,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,So I hope you'll \Nhelp her out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.65,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.58,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,No... No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.17,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.12,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:10.48,Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnBastard\b0\fry-7\bord1.5\fs28\fax-0.03\blur0.5\frz352.48\c&H446B85&\pos(796,243)\3c&H0E2B3F&}The Hollow \NBlue Eyes of Yomi \Nat Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.99,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:36.08,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,My, it's unusual to see \Na boy your age here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.10,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,Are you a customer? Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.43,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.00,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,Are you a junior high student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.25,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll give you half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:44.89,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.66,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,But please, take your \Ntime looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.10,Default,Amane,0,0,0,,I have no other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:28.39,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Fancy meeting \Nyou here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.31,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.62,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I was on my way home \Nfrom the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:37.50,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,and I just happened to walk by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.73,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What about you? \NDidn't you go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.95,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I only go when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.24,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It looks like I won't \Nhave to be readmitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,After that accident... \Nhow's the class been doing?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.02,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,They're all terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.69,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,They think it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.63,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,"It's begun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.31,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Deep down, they may \Nhave only half-believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.26,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:14.15,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Despite what they told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I don't think they fully believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.60,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But it looks like it really is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:30.48,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'd say it's 100% likely \Nthat it's already begun.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:38.78,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Sakakibara, you still don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.53,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're better off that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:44.28,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's best if you never find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Once you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:50.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What on Earth \Nhappened to class 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Are you going back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.18,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:12:00.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I probably shouldn't show up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.65,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.87,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, Misa—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.47,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.19,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what \NI want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.69,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Why? Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.90,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.57,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.81,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.95,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,It's just a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.96,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I've been getting \Nthem a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.68,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,It's pretty annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:11.91,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Maybe you're just exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.43,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.92,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:28.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You said there's a right time to \Nfind out about everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:31.09,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How can I know when that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.53,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.33,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Which class were you \Nin during ninth grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.27,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,During ninth grade...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.67,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Class 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:52.14,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So people talked about class 3 being cursed back then too?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.17,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.31,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,It was 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:01.29,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,You're going to school \Ntomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:03.99,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Remember the tips I gave \Nyou to prepare for Yomi North?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:04.69,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.79,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Including the third one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.18,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Of course. And the fourth, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:14.91,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The third one was to always uphold the class rules, right?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.28,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yes. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:20.99,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Er, um... What was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.25,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The third thing \NI needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.30,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:30.69,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Always uphold the class \Nrules. Which means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.91,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I really am exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.90,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:38.93,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.43,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why—?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:43.10,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.94,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I can't stand that damn bird!
