Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.13,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\an8}What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:25.55,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.87,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.68,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Are you on lunch break right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.61,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.73,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.34,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Do you have time to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.23,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Do you realize what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.90,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:35.78,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I wanted to check with \Nyou on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:37.91,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}We have enough to worry about as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.63,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Check on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:43.81,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,About that Mei girl you told me about yesterday. Misaki Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.46,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Does she really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.68,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.34,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Is she nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.96,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.32,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:57.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,She didn't come \Nto school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:58.89,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,So she's not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:01.71,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.70,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,I spoke to my \Nbrother last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.29,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,He refuses to talk about \Nthe incident 26 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.29,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,or the accident last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.36,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,But when I asked \Nhim about Mei,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.20,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,his demeanor suddenly \Nchanged, and he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.45,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,"What are you talking about?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.60,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,"There's no girl like \Nthat in our class!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.46,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,He was incredibly stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,That's... not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.18,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,But he was dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.91,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,He has no reason to lie.
